Female Unfezant.desc: Females of this species are very capable fliers, particularly notable for their stamina. They also take longer to adjust to people.
This Pokémon is intelligent and intensely proud. People will sit up and take notice if you become the Trainer of one.

Male Unfezant.desc: Unfezant are exceptional fliers. The females are known for their stamina, while the males outclass them in terms of speed.
